00:50:45.545 --> 00:50:49.740
AUDIENCE: What's a useful way
to view emotions, in general,

00:50:49.740 --> 00:50:51.060
in a balanced way?

00:50:51.060 --> 00:50:54.320
In the sense that
I'm not particularly

00:50:54.320 --> 00:50:55.770
in touch with my
own emotions, it

00:50:55.770 --> 00:50:58.817
might take some effort to
detect and be aware of them.

00:50:58.817 --> 00:51:01.400
And some people I know are very
much driven by their emotions,

00:51:01.400 --> 00:51:03.150
and they're very
present and at the front

00:51:03.150 --> 00:51:06.360
of their consciousness.

00:51:06.360 --> 00:51:10.930
And so I tend to think that
with less emotional drive,

00:51:10.930 --> 00:51:12.597
I act more rationally
or more carefully.

00:51:12.597 --> 00:51:14.055
DZOGCHEN PONLOP
RINPOCHE: Oh, I see

00:51:14.055 --> 00:51:15.960
AUDIENCE: But maybe
that's not necessarily

00:51:15.960 --> 00:51:17.740
a positive balanced way.

00:51:17.740 --> 00:51:20.540
What's a good way, you
would say, to view emotions?

00:51:25.110 --> 00:51:27.540
DZOGCHEN PONLOP RINPOCHE:
I think it's no problem.

00:51:27.540 --> 00:51:30.820
If there is no emotion,
it's good news.

00:51:30.820 --> 00:51:33.130
I mean, no bad emotions,
it's good news.

00:51:33.130 --> 00:51:35.370
There's no problem with that.

00:51:35.370 --> 00:51:38.780
But if you are intentionally
blocking out emotion thinking

00:51:38.780 --> 00:51:40.800
it's not good to
have emotions, then

00:51:40.800 --> 00:51:43.010
I think there's a problem there.

00:51:43.010 --> 00:51:46.430
If the emotions are coming,
and you have this presence of,

00:51:46.430 --> 00:51:50.740
let's say, anger all the time
or some sense of jealousy,

00:51:50.740 --> 00:51:53.850
then it's good to
connect with that energy

00:51:53.850 --> 00:51:59.280
rather than pushing it down,
or rather than thinking

00:51:59.280 --> 00:52:02.580
some philosophically or
religiously that this is not

00:52:02.580 --> 00:52:05.150
right or not a
good thing to have.

00:52:05.150 --> 00:52:07.540
But, actually, the energy
of anger is beautiful.

00:52:07.540 --> 00:52:09.170
It's positive.

00:52:09.170 --> 00:52:10.610
There's nothing wrong with that.

00:52:10.610 --> 00:52:13.540
So the balance here
is if they're present,

00:52:13.540 --> 00:52:17.560
appreciate them and try
to work with that energy.

00:52:17.560 --> 00:52:19.680
And when they're not
present, appreciate

00:52:19.680 --> 00:52:23.450
the absence of the
emotions and then

00:52:23.450 --> 00:52:26.810
work with the rational
mind and what have you.

00:52:26.810 --> 00:52:31.440
So not invite them necessarily
when they're not there,

00:52:31.440 --> 00:52:34.190
but then not reject them
when they're present.

00:52:34.190 --> 00:52:37.090
That's the balance I think.

